data.description: Nestled in the serene and family-friendly neighborhood of Westwood Heights, this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. This property is ideal for those who appreciate both the quiet suburban life and the ease of access to local amenities. 204 Mulberry Way is more than just a house; it's a place to call home. Outdoor Living: Enjoy the Georgia sunshine in the backyard, complete with a spacious patio area - ideal for barbecues, outdoor activities, and even fishing. With its inviting ambiance, and prime location, this property is a standout offering in the Rincon real estate market. Also, it has one of the best school districts.  Thirty minutes from the historic Savannah Downtown.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours.
